init_text: Following World War III, all the nations of the world agreed to 50 years of strict isolation from one another in order to prevent additional conflicts. 50 years later, the United States comes out of exile, only to learn that no one else went into isolation.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: As a result, China has become the most powerful nation on Earth.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: In the process of doing so, they attempt to overthrow the government of China and replace it with a new one.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: In retaliation, China declares war on the United States.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The United States government, in an attempt to save the country, takes drastic measures.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: In exchange for the United States' surrender, China will not continue on to conquer the world.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The United States agrees to the terms.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The United States is put under Chinese rule.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: English is no longer taught in schools.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The United States is heavily censored by the Chinese government.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: Instead, the Chinese empire has sponsored a new futuristic sport.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: It is a sport that consists of two teams battling it out with laser beams.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The Chinese empire is pleased with their new acquisition.
